translation: Thou art Motionless Lord! Thou art Unfathomable Lord.42.
Thou art Immeasurable Lord! Thou art the Treasure Lord!
Thou art Manifold Lord! Thou art the Only one Lord! 43.
Salutation to Thee O Universally-Honoured Lord! Salutation to Thee O the Treasure Lord!
Salutation to Thee O Greatest Lord! Salutation to Thee O Garbless Lord! 44.

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਕਾਲ ਕਾਲੇ || ਨਮੋ, ਸਰਬ ਪਾਲੇ ||
transliteration: Namo Kaal Kaale|| Namo Sarab Paale||
translation: Salutation to Thee O Death-Destroyer Lord! Salutation to Thee O Sustainer Lord!

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਸਰਬ ਗੳੁਣੇ || ਨਮੋ, ਸਰਬ ਭੳੁਣੇ ||੪੫||
transliteration: Namo Sarab Gaddde|| Namo Sarab Bhaoune||45||
translation: Salutation to Thee O All-Pervasive Lord! Salutation to Thee O Sustainer Lord!45.
Salutation to Thee O Limitless Lord! Salutation to Thee O Masterless Lord!

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਭਾਨ ਭਾਨੇ || ਨਮੋ, ਮਾਨ ਮਾਨੇ ||੪੬||
transliteration: Namo Bhaan Bhaane|| Namo Maan Maane||46||
translation: Salutation to Thee O Omnipotent Lord! Salutation to Thee O Greatest Sun Lord!46.

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਚੰਦ੍ਰ ਚੰਦ੍ਰੇ || ਨਮੋ, ਭਾਨ ਭਾਨੇ ||
transliteration: Namo Channdra Channdre|| Namo Bhaan Bhaane||
translation: Salutation to Thee O Moon-Soverieign Lord! Salutation to Thee O Sun-Sovereign Lord!

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਗੀਤ ਗੀਤੇ ਨਮੋ, ਤਾਨ ਤਾਨੇ ||੪੭||
transliteration: Namo Goot Goote|| Namo Taan Taane||47||
translation: Salutation to Thee O Supreme Song Lord! Salutation to Thee O Supreme Tune Lord! 47.

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਨਿਰਤ ਨਿਰਤੇ ਨਮੋ, ਨਾਦ ਨਾਦੇ ||
transliteration: Namo Nritt Nritte|| Namo Naad Naade||
translation: Salutation to Thee O Supreme Dance Lord! Salutation to Thee O Supreme Sound Lord!

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਪਾਨ ਪਾਨੇ ਨਮੋ, ਬਾਦ ਬਾਦੇ ||੪੮||
transliteration: Namo Paan Paane|| Namo Baad Baade||48||
translation: Salutation to Thee O Water-Essence Lord! Salutation to Thee O Air-Essence Lord! 48.
